title: League Of Legends Singers
body:
Hey,
So after watching Instalok and Syraphic, I really started enjoying league parodies and league singers, can anyone recommend me some good ones? I would prefer them to be less popular aswell but just recommend whoever ^ - ^ Thanks in advance,
Your sincerely,
Talwyn

replies.body: Falconshiled' this is war series is amazing, and they do some pretty good covers and parodies for league and originals.
